<h1>@Vte{{}}@HI{{miru}}</h1>

<h2> Formation </h2>

<strong>@Vte{{}}@HI{{miru}}</strong>

<h2> Definition </h2>

<strong>@Vte{{}}@HI{{miru}}</strong> means to make an attempt at doing something to see what happens or to see what it is like.
It can also mean that the attempt is a trial.


